          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot (with a matching lid) over a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>chicken breast strips</strong> and <strong>chopped pepper</strong> with your <strong>peri peri spice mix</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and cook for 1 min or until the butter has melted</p>",
