    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>white long grain rice </strong>with 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[530ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [700ml] </span><strong>cold</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>water</strong>,<strong> </strong>your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
